### Manager Approve Request
PATCH http://localhost:4000/leaves/requests/REQUEST_ID/manager-approve?managerId=MANAGER_ID

### HR Finalize Request (Approve)
PATCH http://localhost:4000/leaves/requests/REQUEST_ID/hr-finalize?hrId=HR_ID&decision=approve&allowNegative=false

### HR Finalize Request (Override Negative Balance)
PATCH http://localhost:4000/leaves/requests/REQUEST_ID/hr-finalize?hrId=HR_ID&decision=approve&allowNegative=true

### Cancel Request
PATCH http://localhost:4000/leaves/requests/REQUEST_ID/cancel?employeeId=693a7f807e07119e5fd6a992

### Attempt to Approve Cancelled Request (Should Fail)
PATCH http://localhost:4000/leaves/requests/REQUEST_ID/hr-finalize?hrId=HR_ID&decision=approve

